  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1 \u0dc4\u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Severe Corona from four other areas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Chandima Jeewandara, Head of the Department of Allergy Immunology and Cell Biology, University of Sri Jayawardenepura, said that the BA 5 sub-type of Covid, which is spreading rapidly in the world, has been found in four other areas of the island.",
        "He said that sixty-seven biofilm samples taken from those areas were tested and 60 of them were found to contain this severe corona sub-variety.",
        "He also mentioned that other Omicron subtypes were found in the other seven samples.",
        "The biofilm samples of people infected with Covid-19 taken from the areas of Colombo, Gampaha, Kurunegala and Puttalam have been tested.",
        "The fast-spreading BA5 subtype of Covid was previously found in several areas.",
        "A group of researchers including Professor Chandima Jeevandara conducted genetic analysis tests on these biofilm samples received by the health departments."
      ],
